overview: Mentality team riders Dan MacFarlane, Tyler Kelly, and Joe Moore unleash their technical style of skateboarding on the streets of Houston, Texas and Leeds, UK.  Watch as true underground skate spots get dismantled by a barrage of original and creative skateboard tricks and combinations.
tagline: Mentality team riders Dan MacFarlane, Tyler Kelly, and Joe Moore unleash their technical style of skateboarding on the streets of Houston, Texas and Leeds, UK.
title: Skateboarding Realms
